indexes.index_definition: CREATE INDEX idx_invoice_items_legacy_currency ON public.invoice_items_legacy USING btree (currency) WHERE (currency IS NOT NULL)

CREATE INDEX idx_invoice_items_legacy_invoice ON public.invoice_items_legacy USING btree (invoices_legacy_id)

CREATE INDEX idx_invoice_items_legacy_unit_of_measure ON public.invoice_items_legacy USING btree (unit_of_measure) WHERE (unit_of_measure IS NOT NULL)
